imagenes.descripcion: The China Quick Guide Rail Clamp Woodworking F Clamp 120mm-400mm is a quick clamp for guide rail systems and MFT. This red-colored tool allows for quick clamping and is ideal for woodworking jobs that require precision.

The profile contour gauge is a versatile tool for construction, carpentry and tiling. It allows you to duplicate or trace the shape of objects, which is useful when you need to cut materials to fit irregular shapes. By pressing the gauge against the object, the pins adjust to form an outline of the object. This outline can then be traced onto the material to be cut, ensuring a precise fit.

The WORX WX082L 4V ZipSnip Cordless Electric Scissors are efficient and easy to use. They run on a 4V MaxLithium battery and have safety features. They are portable, weighing only 1 pound, and can cut a wide range of materials.

Chinese garden tool set, FiveJoy. This is an 11-piece basic kit made of durable aluminum alloy. It comes with a garden bag for easy storage and transport. The tools in this set are designed for heavy gardening jobs and feature ergonomic handles for comfort. This set can be a great gift for both men and women who enjoy gardening.
The Swpeet kit includes 3 Chinese glass working tools: glass cutting pliers, glass breaker pliers and a glass cutter with oil reservoir. It is ideal for both beginners and glass professionals.

The Drillpro 600mm China Woodworking Line Scriber T-Ruler is a useful tool for marking and measuring in woodworking. Its aluminum alloy construction ensures durability, while the cross rule marking gauge with 1mm holes helps with accurate measurements. It is a great tool for both professional carpenters and do-it-yourselfers.

The Double Headed Sheet Metal Nibbler China is a metal cutter with drill attachment. It comes with an additional punch and die, a cutting hole attachment and a step drill bit. This tool is perfect for cutting straights, curves and circles. The color of this particular model is gold.

This tool is designed for painting edges and trim. It is a patented design that attaches to any 2-inch brush, providing a clean, precise edge. This tool can be very useful for both professional painters and do-it-yourselfers, as it can significantly reduce the time and effort required for edging and trimming tasks.

The DEWALT 20V MAX cutting tool (DCS438B) is a 3-in-1 power tool designed for cutting difficult materials. It is brushless, which means it runs cooler and more efficiently. It has a built-in LED work light, useful for working in low light conditions. This is a tool-only product, which means no battery or charger is included.

The Universal Adjustable Bench Top Adjustable Hand Planer with 2-inch blade is a tool designed for precision woodworking. This hand planer is adjustable and features a 2-inch blade, making it versatile for a variety of woodworking tasks. It is ideal for smoothing and flattening wood surfaces, and its adjustable nature allows for a customized planing experience.

The DISFRUTA DEWOOD XK4 PRO MAX pocket hole jig is an adjustable woodworking tool made of aluminum alloy. It comes with a drill guide and features a stabilizing bar and stop lock for greater accuracy and control during use.

Masonry tutors for the construction of brick walls. These are tools used in construction, specifically masonry, to ensure that bricks are laid evenly and in a straight line. They are made of high quality stainless steel, which is durable and rust resistant.

The DEWALT 20V Max XR Oscillating Multi-Tool is a high-performance tool with a 3-speed selector. It runs on a 20V Max Lithium Ion Battery. It has a quick swap lever for easy blade changes and a lock-out switch for safety.

Automatic cordless garden pruner. This is a rechargeable garden tool designed for pruning branches. Electric pruning shears make gardening work easier and more efficient. This battery operated model means you can work for long periods of time without having to recharge.

The Chinese window polishing kit is a set of tools for removing scratches from windshields and windows. It contains a wax polishing pad and polishing powder. With this kit, you can effectively remove and polish scratches from the glass surface to improve the appearance of your car. Follow the instructions for safe and effective use.

VEIKO Aluminum Alloy 300mm Angle Positioning T Square Posi Lock Chinese Ruler is an accurate measuring tool. It features an adjustable nut design to change the angle of the ruler. The user simply presses the head to the desired angle. Both edges of the blade are laser engraved. The thin, satin aluminum alloy blade is easy to read and ideal for drawing parallel and angled lines.
NIUPIKA 2KG Chinese metal melting furnace is a small jewelry melting equipment. It has a power of 1400W and can reach temperatures up to 1100℃. It is suitable for 220V and 110V power supply.

Shutoff valve set designed for spray painting tools. It features a Graco airless spray adapter gasket, making it compatible with Wagner and Titan airless spray gun paint tools. This valve set can be a valuable addition to your painting equipment, providing precise control of paint flow and helping to prevent unwanted overspray.

The DIY professional Chinese Chinese power tool set includes a power wrench, water gun, power saw, angle grinder and electric hammer drill. Each tool has its own unique capabilities for a variety of tasks.

The 12Pcs/15Pcs 1/4 6mm 8mm Shank Router Bit Set Router Bit is a set of Chinese tools designed for woodworking. These tools are used for trimming, grooving and engraving wood. They are made of carbide, a material known for its durability and wear resistance. The set includes bits with 1/4, 6 mm and 8 mm shank sizes, which provide versatility for different woodworking tasks. This set is ideal for DIY woodworking projects.

The kit of 2 ratcheting quick release Chinese joinery clamps is an essential tool for any woodworker. These clamps allow for quick and precise adjustment, making them ideal for a variety of woodworking projects. The ratcheting mechanism allows for easy adjustment and release of the clamp.

The mortar spray gun is a valuable tool in construction. It is used to apply mortar or stucco to walls quickly and efficiently. The tool works by loading the reservoir with the material and using compressed air to spray it onto the surface. Depending on the accessories used, it can also be used for other tasks such as welding or painting.

The China Universal Cutting Plate Set for Electric Drill is a sturdy accessory that cuts metal. It can work with sheets of iron, steel, copper, and aluminum up to 1.5 mm thick. It's compatible with common electric drills and turns the drill into an electric cutter.

The SKYMEN JP-010S is a 2L digital ultrasonic cleaner equipped with a heating timer. This 60W ultrasonic machine is ideal for cleaning a wide variety of items, such as dental tools, watches, eyeglasses and coins. It operates on 110 V and includes a US plug. The heating function helps to enhance the cleaning effect. Remember to follow the manufacturer's instructions for safe and effective use.

Multi-angle China Ruler: Allows drawing angular lines at 45, 90, and 135 degrees. Drilling Ruler: Has specially designed holes for precise drawing of different lines. High-Quality Subtlety Ruler: Made of high-quality aluminum alloy, wear-resistant and corrosion-resistant. Precise Woodworking Ruler: Has clear and precise scale in inches and metrics. T Track Ruler for Vertical Measurement: Marked with depth measurement units for vertical measurements.

Metal carving tool set, this collection of stamping tools composed of metal gouges and chisels is suitable for jewelry. These tools are typically used for carving and working on metal surfaces. They are often used by jewelers, artisans and craft enthusiasts to create intricate designs and patterns on various metal surfaces.

Set of 12 triangle-shaped PVC paint stands. These stands are compact and portable, making them ideal for DIY projects. They are an essential tool for any painting project, as they allow you to raise the workpiece off the floor or table, making it easier to paint the edges and prevent paint from sticking to the work surface.

The 12V/24V 125mm Chinese 5-speed electric tile trowel is a power tool designed for tiling tasks. It operates at 5 different speeds, allowing you to adjust the speed according to your specific needs. This machine also features a vibrating suction mechanism, which can help ensure that tiles are laid evenly and securely. The tool is equipped with an LED light, which can be useful when working in low light conditions. It is designed to work with ceramic tiles, which makes it a great choice for both professional contractors and do-it-yourselfers.

The carpenter's planer for wood chamfer is a tool designed for woodworking. This hand planer is used to plane corners and cut wood, making it ideal for woodworking jobs that require precision. Chamfer refers to a cut that is not perpendicular to the face of the workpiece, which can give a more aesthetically pleasing finish.

The pocket hole joint clamp is a useful tool for woodworking. This clamp, also known as a slant hole pull clip, allows you to clamp and align pieces of wood to drill slant pocket holes accurately. It is an essential accessory for any woodworker using the pocket hole technique in their projects.

The MARSHALLTOWN finishing trowel is versatile with rounded and square edges. It is made of high quality tempered steel with a lightweight aluminum alloy backing. The 16 X 4 Rounded Curved Handle is available with DuraSoft®, DuraCork® or wood handles.

The china electric wire cutting pliers are durable and useful for cutting wires. Made of chrome-vanadium steel, they are suitable for various applications, including electrical installation and electronic repair. They have a lightweight design and insulated handles for easy handling.

The adjustable-temperature electric wood planer is a versatile woodworking tool. It allows you to customize the temperature, making it suitable for different types of wood and various projects. This tool can be used for marking, allowing you to leave your unique mark on your creations. It is also ideal for wood burning, a popular woodworking technique that involves engraving designs into wood with a hot tool.

Brush kit for Dremel style rotary power tools is a handy accessory that can enhance the versatility of your rotary tool. This kit typically includes a planer attachment that can be used to trim material from a workpiece. It is ideal for tasks such as trimming door edges, planing wood for a better fit or even creating decorative effects in woodworking. The planer attachment is designed to be compatible with Dremel-type rotary tools, which are known for their high speed and precision. This makes it a useful addition to your tool collection if you frequently work with wood or other materials that need to be planed.

The swooshes and small stitches tool is used for stitch art. It is made of stainless steel, with a sharp end for scratching guides on projects and the golden end for small dots. It is perfect for drawing lines, fine details, flowers, patterns, etc.

Grass Trimmer Head Steel Wheel Garden Weed Brush Brushcutter Trimmer. 6/8 inch brushcutter brush designed for garden mowers and power tools. It is a sturdy and effective tool that can make your gardening tasks easier and more precise.
